<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:14:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>只有一个人知道内塔尼亚胡是否偿还了他的百万富翁朋友的贷款 - 但他并没有说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/only-one-man-knows-if-netanyahu-repaid-loan-from-millionaire-friend-and-hes-not-saying/0000018e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡获得了从斯宾塞·帕特里奇那里贷款的许可，后者此前曾给他买过雪茄和西装。这笔贷款是由总理亲自挑选的国家审计长批准的，该审计长应该通过内塔尼亚胡的资产和利息披露来监督还款，而公众无法获得这些信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/only-one-man-knows-if-netanyahu-repaid-loan-from-millionaire-friend-and-hes-not-saying/0000018e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</guid></item><item><title>“这是一场残酷的富人之间的战争。以色列在加沙的战斗形式异常浪费”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-war-of-cruel-rich-people-israels-form-of-combat-in-gaza-is-unusually-wasteful/0000018e-1aa8-d1cc-abfe-dfadbc010000</link><description>加沙战争中出现的弹药相关问题将在稍后进行调查。与此同时，他们正在决定军队的战略，并使以色列完全依赖其美国盟友</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-war-of-cruel-rich-people-israels-form-of-combat-in-gaza-is-unusually-wasteful/0000018e-1aa8-d1cc-abfe-dfadbc010000</guid></item><item><title>正统派政党达成解决拜特谢梅什市长选举决选的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/haredi-parties-cut-deal-to-resolve-run-off-in-beit-shemesh-mayoral-election/0000018e-1a83-d7d3-abce-7aab6cad0000</link><description>Degel Hatorah、Agudat Yisrael 和 Shas 之间的合作协议预计也将对 Bnei Brak 的市政政治和下一次议会选举产生影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 20:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/haredi-parties-cut-deal-to-resolve-run-off-in-beit-shemesh-mayoral-election/0000018e-1a83-d7d3-abce-7aab6cad0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙迫切需要援助。拜登找到解决办法了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-07/ty-article/.highlight/gaza-desperately-needs-aid-is-bidens-new-emergency-port-plan-the-answer/0000018e-19ed-dec4-abcf-dfefa9150000</link><description>由于未能确保停火，紧急港口将成为拜登在国情咨文演讲期间发表以色列-加沙言论的核心内容。随着斋月的临近，每一分钟的风险都呈指数级增长</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 20:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-07/ty-article/.highlight/gaza-desperately-needs-aid-is-bidens-new-emergency-port-plan-the-answer/0000018e-19ed-dec4-abcf-dfefa9150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列获准参加下个月的欧洲歌唱大赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-given-permission-to-participate-in-next-months-eurovision-contest/0000018e-1a3d-d8fb-abff-5f3f935c0000</link><description>经过数周的不确定性和对以色列必须待在家里的真正担忧之后，欧洲广播联盟批准了《飓风》的歌词，该歌词将于周日在 Kan 11 的特别广播中首播</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 19:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-given-permission-to-participate-in-next-months-eurovision-contest/0000018e-1a3d-d8fb-abff-5f3f935c0000</guid></item><item><title>今年妇女节，加沙的巴勒斯坦妇女正在帐篷里制作经期产品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-womens-day-palestinian-women-in-gaza-are-making-period-products-out-of-tents/0000018e-1980-d7d3-abce-79a9bfa90000</link><description>加沙妇女在面临水危机时剪掉头发、在没有麻醉的情况下剖腹产并用废料制作经期产品，在不可能的情况下展现了力量和聪明才智</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 19:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-womens-day-palestinian-women-in-gaza-are-making-period-products-out-of-tents/0000018e-1980-d7d3-abce-79a9bfa90000</guid></item><item><title>OSINT 揭示了自 10 月 7 日以来美国向以色列空运武器的规模空前</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/open-source-intelligence-reveals-the-unprecedented-extent-of-u-s-arms-airlifts-to-israel/0000018e-1976-d021-adef-9f77c76c0000</link><description>据报道，自加沙战争爆发以来，拜登政府已向以色列秘密出售了 100 笔武器。公开的飞行数据显示了它是如何展开的</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/open-source-intelligence-reveals-the-unprecedented-extent-of-u-s-arms-airlifts-to-israel/0000018e-1976-d021-adef-9f77c76c0000</guid></item><item><title>战时的斋月和阿克萨清真寺：加沙战争将如何影响以色列和巴勒斯坦的关键热点？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-timeline/.premium/ramadan-and-al-aqsa-in-wartime-the-gaza-war-and-a-key-israeli-palestinian-flashpoint/0000018e-0ef9-d203-a9ce-1ef989420000</link><description>随着斋月下周开始，本已动荡的中东将面临另一场考验，重点是耶路撒冷的阿克萨清真寺。加沙战争将如何影响以色列和巴勒斯坦的关键热点？ |国土报解释</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-timeline/.premium/ramadan-and-al-aqsa-in-wartime-the-gaza-war-and-a-key-israeli-palestinian-flashpoint/0000018e-0ef9-d203-a9ce-1ef989420000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 153 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-153/0000018e-19e2-dec4-abcf-dfeb7b140000</link><description>拜登宣布美国将在加沙建立临时港口以接收大量援助物资 ■ 哈马斯领导人对停火条款存在分歧 ■ 哈马斯高级官员称以色列“挫败”调解人达成协议的努力 ■ 谈判将至少持续到第一次消息人士称，斋月一周 ■ 以色列国防军开始对导致哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的失误进行内部调查 ■ 战争结束 153 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-153/0000018e-19e2-dec4-abcf-dfeb7b140000</guid></item><item><title>“我并不爱很多地方，只爱以色列。在德国，即使我不是犹太人，我也会去犹太教堂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/im-not-in-love-with-many-places-only-with-israel/0000018e-19a5-dec4-abcf-dfaf4da00000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：十几岁的克劳斯爱上了一个以色列男孩，最终爱上了以色列。他最近的一次访问是做志愿者并帮助南方的农民</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 16:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/im-not-in-love-with-many-places-only-with-israel/0000018e-19a5-dec4-abcf-dfaf4da00000</guid></item><item><title>拜登将宣布在加沙建立紧急港口以便利援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-gaza-war-set-to-feature-in-bidens-state-of-the-union-address/0000018e-1930-d021-adef-9f375a490000</link><description>拜登将在周四晚的国情咨文演讲中宣布，美国军方将领导紧急任务，建立加沙港口以运送援助物资，这可以说是其总统任期内最重要的演讲——17名被哈马斯俘虏或杀害的美国人的亲属在一旁观看</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 16:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-gaza-war-set-to-feature-in-bidens-state-of-the-union-address/0000018e-1930-d021-adef-9f375a490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队开始调查 10 月 7 日之前的故障</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-begins-investigation-of-failures-leading-up-to-october-7/0000018e-1905-d1cc-abfe-dfad95730000</link><description>以色列国防军的调查将审查从 2018 年到 2023 年 10 月 10 日期间，哈马斯致命袭击后重新夺回对加沙边境周边社区的控制</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 14:42:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-begins-investigation-of-failures-leading-up-to-october-7/0000018e-1905-d1cc-abfe-dfad95730000</guid></item><item><title>因意大利政府反对而被撤销西岸市长大使职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-mayors-ambassadorship-revoked-following-italian-govt-opposition/0000018e-18d6-d8fb-abff-5dde377e0000</link><description>意大利政府对任命本尼·卡什里尔（Benny Kasriel）担任以色列驻该国特使表示担忧，因为他住在约旦河西岸。谈判未果，外交部发布了该职位的内部招标</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-mayors-ambassadorship-revoked-following-italian-govt-opposition/0000018e-18d6-d8fb-abff-5dde377e0000</guid></item><item><title>国家检察官阻止对父亲被指控强奸未成年人的以色列 MK 进行审讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-prevents-interrogation-of-mk-whose-father-is-accused-of-raping-minors/0000018e-184b-d8fb-abff-5d4b7f170000</link><description>MK Yaakov Tessler 涉嫌向一名 15 岁受害者支付封口费，该受害者据称被 Tessler 的父亲强奸。尽管案件已搁置六个月，但他的调查尚未获得国家检察官的授权</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-prevents-interrogation-of-mk-whose-father-is-accused-of-raping-minors/0000018e-184b-d8fb-abff-5d4b7f170000</guid></item><item><title>由于战争，以色列部长取消了一年一度的独立日烟花表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-nixes-annual-independence-day-fireworks-show-due-to-war/0000018e-188a-d1cc-abfe-dfafc31e0000</link><description>利库德集团部长米里·雷格夫对鉴于严峻的形势，第76届独立日仪式未能按照传统举行表示遗憾。两年前，烟花表演也因患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD) 的退伍军人的反对而被取消</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-nixes-annual-independence-day-fireworks-show-due-to-war/0000018e-188a-d1cc-abfe-dfafc31e0000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，已有 27 名加沙被拘留者在以色列军事设施的拘留期间死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/27-gaza-detainees-died-in-custody-at-israeli-army-facilities-since-the-start-of-the-war/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bbaa370000</link><description>返回加沙的被拘留者作证称，他们受到了严酷的待遇，包括士兵和审讯期间的殴打和虐待。以色列国防军发言人表示，军方已对死亡事件展开调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/27-gaza-detainees-died-in-custody-at-israeli-army-facilities-since-the-start-of-the-war/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bbaa370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列奖司法小组要求加入高等法院，反对教育部长取消大多数奖项的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-panel-asks-to-join-petitions-against-ministers-decision-to-nix-most-awards/0000018e-180d-d1cc-abfe-dfadb2a20000</link><description>司法小组表示，应该允许它成为请愿书的一方，“因为它拥有大量事实信息，如果没有这些信息，在保密的幌子下，不得将其提交高等法院”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:41:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-panel-asks-to-join-petitions-against-ministers-decision-to-nix-most-awards/0000018e-180d-d1cc-abfe-dfadb2a20000</guid></item><item><title>当人类离开时，乌鸦会玩耍吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/do-crows-play-when-the-humans-are-away/0000018e-1821-d8fb-abff-5d2be6010000</link><description>以色列在新冠病毒大流行期间进行的一项研究分析了人类（据称）被限制在家里时三种鸟类的行为，结果表明生活在我们中间的野生动物适应得非常快</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:49:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/do-crows-play-when-the-humans-are-away/0000018e-1821-d8fb-abff-5d2be6010000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡的统治下，以色列还会遭受多少死亡和灾难？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/how-many-more-deaths-and-disasters-will-israel-endure-under-netanyahus-watch/0000018e-1538-d792-a7be-3db8cd320000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理助长了宗教与国家之间的腐败关系，导致梅龙灾难的发生。他对调查委员会报告的回应反映了报告中描述的腐败文化</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/how-many-more-deaths-and-disasters-will-israel-endure-under-netanyahus-watch/0000018e-1538-d792-a7be-3db8cd320000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩正在等待加沙停火以结束与以色列的争端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-is-waiting-for-a-ceasefire-in-gaza-to-end-its-dispute-with-israel/0000018e-15ed-d8fb-abff-55eff96b0000</link><description>美国越来越多地参与以色列北部边境的敌对行动以及这场冲突与加沙战争之间的联系。为了取得成功，华盛顿特使需要内塔尼亚胡和纳斯鲁拉合作</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-is-waiting-for-a-ceasefire-in-gaza-to-end-its-dispute-with-israel/0000018e-15ed-d8fb-abff-55eff96b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>